            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Caelesti Virgini <lb n="2"/>Augustae <expan><abbr>sacr</abbr><ex>um</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/>Nemesianus <expan><abbr>Caes</abbr><ex>aris</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>n</abbr><ex>ostri</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/>servos <note>sic</note> librarius tem<lb break="no" n="5"/>plum a solo &amp;lt;p=R&amp;gt;ecunia su<lb break="no" n="6"/>a ex voto fecit 
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Inschriftfeld in Form einer tabula ansata. Hedera am Ende von Z. 6. (B): von Finály; AE 1913; Jánó: Abweichungen in der Lesung.</p>
            </div>
